{"word":"Watchman","slug":"watchman","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Watchman</b> A sentinel.<br/> On the walls:<br/> - Of cities<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=22&chapter=3&verse=3'>Son 3:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=22&chapter=5&verse=7'>Son 5:7</a> <br/> - Of Jerusalem<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=13&verse=34'>2Sa 13:34</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=18&verse=25'>2Sa 18:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=4&verse=9'>Neh 4:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=7&verse=3'>Neh 7:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=52&verse=8'>Isa 52:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=62&verse=6'>Isa 62:6</a> <br/> - Of Babylon<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=51&verse=12'>Jer 51:12</a> <br/> On towers<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=9&verse=17'>2Ki 9:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=20&verse=24'>2Ch 20:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=21&verse=12'>Isa 21:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=31&verse=6'>Jer 31:6</a><br/> At the gates of the temple<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=11&verse=7'>2Ki 11:7</a><br/> Alarm of, given by trumpets<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=33&verse=6'>Eze 33:6</a><br/> Unfaithfulness in the discharge of duty of, punished by death<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=33&verse=6'>Eze 33:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=28&verse=14'>Mat 28:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=12&verse=19'>Act 12:19</a>"}]}